WEBVTT

00:05:57.887 --> 00:06:03.136
In 1998, I lost my reputation
and my dignity.

00:06:03.734 --> 00:06:06.321
I lost almost everything.

00:06:07.226 --> 00:06:09.231
And I almost lost my life.

00:06:13.031 --> 00:06:14.809
Let me paint a picture for you.

00:06:17.365 --> 00:06:20.215
It is September of 1998.

00:06:20.866 --> 00:06:23.690
I'm sitting in a windowless office room

00:06:23.714 --> 00:06:26.197
inside the Office
of the Independent Counsel,

00:06:27.213 --> 00:06:30.040
underneath humming fluorescent lights.